<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="{{#if lang}}{{lang}}{{else}}fr{{/if}}">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <title>{{#eq lang "en"}}FASO ADMIN — Approval required{{else}}FASO ADMIN — Approbation requise{{/eq}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f3f6f4;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;">
  <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f3f6f4;padding:32px 0;">
    <tr><td align="center">
      <table width="640" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;padding:28px 32px;border-top:4px solid #FFD700;">
            <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:22px;">FASO ADMIN</h1>
            <p style="margin:6px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#FFD700;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Dual-control approval required{{else}}Approbation dual-control requise{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:32px;color:#222;">
            <p style="font-size:15px;line-height:1.55;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}A privileged role grant request requires your approval as SUPER-ADMIN.{{else}}Une demande d'attribution de rôle privilégié nécessite votre approbation en tant que SUPER-ADMIN.{{/eq}}
            </p>
            <table width="100%" style="margin:20px 0;border-collapse:collapse;background:#fafafa;border:1px solid #eee;border-radius:6px;">
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;color:#666;width:35%;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Requester{{else}}Demandeur{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;"><strong>{{requester}}</strong></td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Target user{{else}}Utilisateur cible{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;">{{target}}</td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:13px;color:#666;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Requested role{{else}}Rôle demandé{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #eee;font-size:14px;">
                <span style="background:#E53935;color:#ffffff;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:4px;font-weight:bold;">{{role}}</span>
              </td></tr>
              <tr><td style="padding:10px;font-size:13px;color:#666;vertical-align:top;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Justification{{else}}Justification{{/eq}}
              </td><td style="padding:10px;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;color:#333;">{{justification}}</td></tr>
            </table>
            <p style="text-align:center;margin:28px 0;">
              <a href="{{approvalLink}}" style="background:#1b5e20;color:#ffffff;padding:14px 32px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:6px;font-weight:bold;display:inline-block;">
                {{#eq lang "en"}}Review &amp; approve{{else}}Examiner et approuver{{/eq}}
              </a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:#888;text-align:center;">
              {{#eq lang "en"}}Approval requires your hardware security key (FIDO2 / PassKey).{{else}}L'approbation nécessite votre clé de sécurité matérielle (FIDO2 / PassKey).{{/eq}}
            </p>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="background:#1b5e20;color:#FFD700;padding:14px 32px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;">
            FASO DIGITALISATION — République du Burkina Faso<br/>
            <a href="https://faso.bf/security" style="color:#FFD700;text-decoration:underline;">https://faso.bf/security</a>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </td></tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
